These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, grapefruit, lime, pear, pineapple, tomato, watermelon
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, rock, r&b, funk, hip-hop, salsa, electronic
7 different games are played: canasta, chess, domino, scrabble, snooker, poker, whist
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, american, turkish, thai, canadian, pakistani, malaysian
 1. the italian is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 2. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the fan of hip-hop is the pakistani##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the italian is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the person eating tomato##1
 7. the malaysian is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 8. the turkish is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 9. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
11. the fan of salsa is the person eating lime##1
12. the italian is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of rock##1
14. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating lime##1
15. the person eating lime is between the fan of metal and the canadian##2
16. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
17. the person eating pear is the canadian##1
18. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
19. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
20. the fan of salsa is the person eating lime##1
21. the person playing whist is on the right of the pakistani##1
22. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the american##1
23. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
24. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
25. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person playing chess##1
26. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Food        | grapefruit | tomato     | lime           | pear          | pineapple  | watermelon | corn         |
| Music-Genre         | electronic  | metal | salsa | r&b   | rock | hip-hop   | funk       |
| Game       | snooker   | canasta  | domino        | poker | chess   | scrabble    | whist |
| Nationality   | malaysian        | thai       | italian           | canadian         | turkish     | pakistani       | american    |

